    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">2.2 Mechanism-Editor:</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2"><image src="2r.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">&#32;</text>Mechanism-Editor </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">You do most of your modelling in <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editors</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Modelelements(Model)-AddMechanism" styleclass="SeeAlso">Add Mechanism-Editor</link><text styleclass="SeeAlso"> - </text><text styleclass="Body Text">when the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Model-Editor</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> is active</text><text styleclass="VariableName">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-ModelElements(Mechanism)-AddMechanism" styleclass="SeeAlso">Add Mechanism-Editor</link><text styleclass="SeeAlso"> - </text><text styleclass="Body Text">in a </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> is active</text><text styleclass="VariableName">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">Mechanism-Editor workspace</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-EDITOR-MECHANISM-EX.ipp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
